OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer is facing mounting
OL,7,Fpressure and a top civil servant is to
OL,8,Fleave their post after it emerged the
OL,9,FForeign Office overruled a security
OL,10,Fvetting process to clear Lord Peter
OL,11,FMandelson to become UK ambassador to
OL,12,Fthe US.
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister and Foreign
OL,15,FSecretary Yvette Cooper have lost
OL,16,Fconfidence in Foreign Office permanent
OL,17,Funder-secretary Sir Olly Robbins over
OL,18,Fthe issue and he will be leaving the
OL,19,Fjob, the Press Association understands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
