FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FSecurity officials initially denied
OL,7,Fthe peer clearance, but Foreign Office
OL,8,Fofficials took the rare step of
OL,9,Foverruling the recommendation.
OL,11,FThe Prime Minister was not aware that
OL,12,Fthe former Labour grandee was granted
OL,13,Fdeveloped vetting against the advice
OL,14,Fof UK Security Vetting until earlier
OL,15,Fthis week, the Government has said.
OL,17,FHe has instructed officials to
OL,18,Festablish the facts about why vetting
OL,19,Fwas granted, and the Foreign Office
OL,20,Fearlier said it is "working urgently"
OL,21,Fto comply.
OL,26,@|D@TOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
