CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FDowning Street sources say the Prime
OL,7,FMinister is "absolutely furious".
OL,9,FReports on Thursday suggested he may
OL,10,Fmake a statement in the Commons on
OL,11,FMonday over the matter but No 10 did
OL,12,Fnot confirm if he would face MPs.
OL,14,FSir Keir is due to face the media on
OL,15,FFriday alongside French President
OL,16,FEmmanuel Macron as he co-hosts a
OL,17,Fsummit on reopening the Strait of
OL,18,FHormuz in Paris, with the pair
OL,19,Fexpected to make a joint statement in
OL,20,Fthe afternoon.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
