PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FDavid Lammy, who was foreign secretary
OL,7,Fwhen Lord Mandelson was appointed,
OL,8,Falso did not know the Foreign Office
OL,9,Fhad overruled the vetting until
OL,10,FThursday afternoon, it is understood.
OL,12,FA report in The Guardian revealed that
OL,13,Fsecurity officials initially denied
OL,14,Fthe peer clearance but that the
OL,15,FForeign Office overruled the
OL,16,Frecommendation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
