FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson later
OL,7,Fconfirmed that "officials in the FCDO"
OL,8,Fhad taken the decision to grant
OL,9,Fdeveloped vetting against the
OL,10,Frecommendation.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister has faced calls to
OL,13,Fstand down over the matter, with
OL,14,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,15,Fcalling it "preposterous" to claim he
OL,16,Fdid not know Lord Mandelson failed
OL,17,Fsecurity vetting.
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@fO]wD@LOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
