OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FLord Mandelson, a political
OL,7,Fappointment rather than a career
OL,8,Fdiplomat, was sacked from his
OL,9,FWashington role last September when
OL,10,Fmore details emerged about his
OL,11,Frelationship with paedophile financier
OL,12,FJeffrey Epstein, who died in 2019.
OL,14,FSir Keir has been under fire over the
OL,15,Fdecision to give Lord Mandelson the
OL,16,Fjob despite it being known that his
OL,17,Fdealings with Epstein continued after
OL,18,Fthe financier's conviction for child
OL,19,Fsex offences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
