PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FQuestions over his judgment
OL,7,Fintensified after the first batch of
OL,8,Fdocuments related to the decision
OL,9,Fpublished last month showed that he
OL,10,Fwas warned before announcing Lord
OL,11,FMandelson's ambassadorship of a
OL,12,F"general reputational risk" over his
OL,13,Fassociation with Epstein.
OL,15,FThat warning stemmed from the first
OL,16,Fpart of the checks, carried out by the
OL,17,FCabinet Office, which was based on
OL,18,Finformation in the public domain at
OL,19,Fthe time.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
