PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FThe second was the highly confidential
OL,7,Fbackground vetting by security
OL,8,Fofficials, which followed the
OL,9,Fannouncement but came before Lord
OL,10,FMandelson took up his role in February
OL,11,F2025.
OL,13,FInformation unearthed in this process
OL,14,F` including any concerns ` is never
OL,15,Fshared with ministers, and the result
OL,16,Fis binary, either clearing the
OL,17,Fcandidate or barring them.
OL,19,FMore documents relating to his
OL,20,Fappointment are yet to be released at
OL,21,Fthe behest of MPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
