CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776395018
OL,3,CTop civil servant ousted after Foreign
OL,4,COffice overruled Mandelson vetting
OL,6,FSir Keir said in February that Lord
OL,7,FMandelson was cleared by security
OL,8,Fvetting, which he criticised for
OL,9,Ffailing to disprove the former Labour
OL,10,Fgrandee's lies.
OL,12,FWhen Morgan McSweeney stepped down as
OL,13,FSir Keir's chief of staff in February,
OL,14,Fhe took "full responsibility" for
OL,15,Fgiving his boss advice that resulted
OL,16,Fin the "wrong" appointment decision,
OL,17,Fwhile also calling for the vetting
OL,18,Fprocess to be "fundamentally
OL,19,Foverhauled".
OL,26,@vD@IOUvD@]O]xD@HOUxD@NO]zD@OOU{D@KO]
